summary:
I use programming languages as tools for resolving real world problems, understanding the solution have to be designed before writing a single line of code. We all know that requirements change over time, so I use continuous integration methods like version control (Git), tickets (Jira) and SOLID design. As for coding, I use Python, PHP or Go for backend systems, and Javascript (React, Redux) for the frontend, both ends communicating through Rest APIs. Databases are a must so I always try to keep the models clean and organized whatever working with SQL or NoSql ddbbs.
Aside from web development, I always like to make personals projects with computer vision (OpenCV) and machine learning tools (PyTorch), improving really fast.

As for my attitude, I have passion for finding solutions and design them no matter what kind of problem I am dealing with, keeping in mind that there are always deadline to meet. Love to learn new technologies and further improve the ones that I already know.
